              "id": "OJS-SC-CVE-001",
              "name": "CVE-2023-33970 - XSS via galley label",
              "shortDescription": {
                "text": "CVE-2023-33970 - XSS via galley label"
              },
              "fullDescription": {
                "text": "OJS versions before 3.3.0-16 are vulnerable to stored XSS through the galley label field. An authenticated user can inject JavaScript via a crafted galley label.\n"
